trans-unit.source: Represents a text effect that can be applied to text objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa um efeito de texto que pode ser aplicado a objetos de texto.

trans-unit.source: The TextEffect object allows you to add effects, such as animations, to text objects, such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>, and <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: O objeto de TextEffect permite-lhe adicionar efeitos, tais como animações, para objetos de texto, tal como <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>, e <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>objetos.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>
